show.description: In a secluded mountain village, women working as schoolteachers are being brutally murdered. Andria and her friend Sasha are newly appointed teachers in the same village. Soon after they arrive, Andria begins having unsettling dreams that seem to reveal the horrors unfolding around them. As fear closes in, Andria is caught by a group targeting female teachers while Sasha narrowly escapes. But the mystery deepens: who are these ruthless killers, and why are they hunting women in this isolated village?
